    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This Thursday October 24th, we’re excited to launch the <strong>AK Roosevelt Capsule</strong> — a limited-edition collection crafted in collaboration with Extracurricular and Anthony Kim, inspired by Los Angeles' beloved Roosevelt Golf Course. This collection isn't just about golf apparel; it's a tribute to a place that holds a special part in Anthony's journey.</p><p>For Anthony, Roosevelt is more than a golf course — it’s where he fell in love with the game. Growing up in LA, he spent countless hours playing there, soaking in the atmosphere, and finding inspiration in the people he met and the challenges he faced. What makes Roosevelt unique isn’t just the game itself, but the sense of community it fosters.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["text_1"],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
