        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The AK Roosevelt Capsule launches <strong>this Thursday</strong> and will be available for just four days. Keep an eye on your inbox for the official release, and be sure to sign up for launch notifications on each product page. Don’t miss your chance to own a piece of Anthony’s story.</p>"
